OL,3,CPostal voting applications open ahead
OL,4,Cof June election
OL,6,FPeople in Jersey can now apply for
OL,7,Fpostal votes ahead of this summer's
OL,8,Felection.
OL,10,FPostal voting is available to all
OL,11,Fislanders who are eligible to vote in
OL,12,Fthe poll which will be held on Sunday
OL,13,F7 June.
OL,15,FIslanders will elect 49 politicians
OL,16,Fwho will serve in the States Assembly
OL,17,Ffor the next four years.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/3
