OL,3,CPostal voting applications open ahead
OL,4,Cof June election
OL,6,FApplications can be downloaded online
OL,7,For collected in-person from parish
OL,8,Fhalls, the Judicial Greffe in the
OL,9,FRoyal Square or the States Greffe at
OL,10,FMorier House.
OL,12,FApplications must be submitted by the
OL,13,Fend of April. This can be done by
OL,14,Fscanning and emailing the signed form
OL,15,Fto VotingApplications@courts.je or to
OL,16,Fthe Judicial Greffe by post.
OL,18,FIslanders are eligible to vote if they:
OL,20,FThis means students from Jersey who
OL,21,Fare studying off-island can still vote.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/3
