OL,3,CPostal voting applications open ahead
OL,4,Cof June election
OL,6,FRebecca Morely-Kirk, Jersey's Judicial
OL,7,FGreffier, said: "Postal voting ensures
OL,8,Fthat every eligible islander can take
OL,9,Fpart in our democratic process ` even
OL,10,Fif life commitments mean it's
OL,11,Fdifficult to make it to the polling
OL,12,Fstation on Election Day.
OL,14,F"Whether you are on-island or not,
OL,15,Fvoters have the option to apply for
OL,16,Fpostal voting.
OL,18,F"Every ballot cast strengthens
OL,19,FJersey's democracy, and postal voting
OL,20,Foffers a convenient way to ensure your
OL,21,FvoiceJis heard and your vote counts."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/3
